[00:33:21.360 --> 00:33:23.460]  好,我們一起祈禱
[00:33:23.460 --> 00:33:26.460]  Let's pray together
[00:33:26.460 --> 00:33:28.160]  Dear Heavenly Father, we thank You
[00:33:28.160 --> 00:33:29.760]  That You know us
[00:33:29.760 --> 00:33:32.860]  That You know what is best for us
[00:33:32.860 --> 00:33:34.160]  And we trust You
[00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:35.860]  Help us to trust You
[00:33:35.860 --> 00:33:37.460]  To follow You
[00:33:37.460 --> 00:33:39.860]  So that Lord, we can glorify You
[00:33:39.860 --> 00:33:42.360]  With our life and with our story
[00:33:42.360 --> 00:33:44.560]  In Christ's name we pray, Amen
